sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Auth as get_current_user
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over F,DB: === 注册 ===
    U->>F: 填写用户名/邮箱/密码
    F->>API: POST /api/auth/register
    API->>API: 校验密码 <= 72 bytes
    API->>DB: INSERT users (bcrypt hash)
    API->>API: 签发 JWT
    API-->>F: Set-Cookie + access_token
    F->>F: 存储认证状态

    Note over F,DB: === 登录 ===
    U->>F: 输入凭据
    F->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API->>DB: SELECT by username
    API->>API: bcrypt.verify
    API-->>F: Set-Cookie + access_token

    Note over F,DB: === 认证中间件 ===
    F->>API: 任何 API 请求
    API->>Auth: Cookie / Bearer 提取 token
    Auth->>Auth: JWT 验证（签名/iss/aud/exp）
    Auth->>DB: 确认 user 存在 & is_active
    Auth-->>API: current_user 注入
    API->>API: Owner 权限校验
    API-->>F: 响应（脱敏后）
